lead_paragraph: Revenue at Euro 2016 has increased by 34 percent to 1.93 billion euros ($2.13 billion) compared to Euro 2012, European soccer's governing body UEFA said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Euro 2016 Revenue Up 34 Percent to 1.93 Billion Euros-UEFA
